<subSubSection id="C31F6781D713FFD981EFFC228E8A5B6E" pageId="5" pageNumber="32" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BBA340AD713FFD981EFFC228E8A5B6E" blockId="5.[174,1232,974,1129]" pageId="5" pageNumber="32">
C o l o r a t i o n. This species differs from 
<taxonomicName id="4C054F89D713FFD983B8FC228E605C8E" authority="(Fabricius, 1793)" baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" baseAuthorityYear="1793" box="[692,1146,974,1001]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Rhyssella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="approximator">
<emphasis id="B971E818D713FFD983B8FC2289AD5C8F" box="[692,951,974,1000]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="32">Rhyssella approximator</emphasis>
(Fabricius, 1793)
</taxonomicName>
in having yellow pterostigma, scutellum, postscutellum and two stripes on mesoscutum. OTI 5.0
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
